      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForAllItems",
        "jsCode": "// The Webhook node delivers the raw Telegram update under .body. Normalize\n// message | edited_message | callback_query into one shape, and DROP anything\n// not from the single authorized operator chat (replaces the Telegram Trigger's\n// restrictToChatIds; Caddy already validated the secret token at the edge). This\n// chat-id check IS the from.id allowlist for callback presses (chatId = cb.from.id).\n// @@CHAT_ID@@ is substituted at install time.\n// HITL (Stage C): a callback whose data is `app:<id>` / `rej:<id>` is an approval\n// press — flag route='approval' + is_approve + action_id so the Switch downstream\n// runs the executor instead of the chat router. Any other update routes to chat.\n// Vision (Stage tg-vision): a message carrying a photo (largest size) or an\n// image/* document flags route='image' + file_id/file_size/mime so the Switch hands\n// it to the tg-vision sub-workflow. A photo with no caption is NO LONGER dropped\n// (previously `if (!text) return []` discarded it).\nconst u = ($input.first().json && $input.first().json.body) || $input.first().json || {};\nconst cb = u.callback_query || null;\nconst msg = u.message || u.edited_message || (cb && cb.message) || {};\nconst isCallback = !!cb;\nlet text = isCallback ? (cb.data || '') : (msg.text || msg.caption || '');\ntext = String(text).trim();\nconst chatId = (msg.chat && msg.chat.id) || (cb && cb.from && cb.from.id) || '';\nif (String(chatId) !== '@@CHAT_ID@@') { return []; }\nlet fileId = '';\nlet fileSize = 0;\nlet fileMime = '';\nif (!isCallback) {\n  if (Array.isArray(msg.photo) && msg.photo.length) {\n    const ph = msg.photo[msg.photo.length - 1] || {};\n    fileId = ph.file_id || '';\n    fileSize = Number(ph.file_size || 0);\n    fileMime = 'image/jpeg';\n  } else if (msg.document && typeof msg.document === 'object' && /^image\\//i.test(String(msg.document.mime_type || ''))) {\n    fileId = msg.document.file_id || '';\n    fileSize = Number(msg.document.file_size || 0);\n    fileMime = String(msg.document.mime_type || '');\n  }\n}\nlet voiceFileId = '';\nlet voiceDuration = 0;\nif (!isCallback && msg.voice && msg.voice.file_id) {\n  voiceFileId = msg.voice.file_id;\n  voiceDuration = Number(msg.voice.duration || 0);\n}\nif (!text && !fileId && !voiceFileId) { return []; }\nconst updateId = Number(u.update_id || 0);\nconst isApproval = isCallback && /^(app|rej):/.test(text);\nconst isApprove = text.slice(0, 4) === 'app:';\nconst actionId = isApproval ? Number(text.split(':')[1]) : null;\nreturn [{ json: { text: text, chat_id: chatId, kind: isCallback ? 'callback_query' : (u.edited_message ? 'edited_message' : 'message'), update_id: updateId, callback_id: (cb && cb.id) || '', message_id: (cb && cb.message && cb.message.message_id) || '', route: (isApproval && Number.isInteger(actionId) && actionId > 0) ? 'approval' : (fileId ? 'image' : (voiceFileId ? 'voice' : 'chat')), is_approve: isApprove, action_id: actionId, file_id: fileId, file_size: fileSize, mime: fileMime, voice_file_id: voiceFileId, voice_duration: voiceDuration } }];"
      },
